</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-146_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-147_">Deliver safer care and better education
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-149_">Respond confidently to regulatory inspections
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-151_">Reduce incidents and performance gaps
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-153_">Build environments where people thrive, not just comply.
</li></ul><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-155_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-41b46b9e-e516-4ff8-844a-6b82e1f3d73e"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Let’s stop asking: <em>“Have they completed the training?”</em><br></span></p><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-158_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-36935eb0-0161-4bdc-8257-63e788ef56f3"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Start asking: <em>“Are they applying it, safely, confidently, and consistently?”</em>
